reviewText: This is a well done teaching tool. I watched it three times in the first week and learned someting each time. Excellent. I plan to start using Johnnie Liliedahl's technique in future oil portraits.

Excellent educational video on painting.  Would purchase more from Liliedahl.  She very informative, and her technique is above and beyond others I have seen.

Michael Kiss

Johnnie is always amazing, and it is no different in this video. This video is no longer available, but has been broken down into two new portrait videos. Both are amazing as well and impart a wealth of information.
